X: 81
T: Christ Jesus Lay In Death's Strong Bands
T: (also known as In Death's Strong Bands)
C: Words: Martin Luther, 1524. Translated by Richard Massie, 1854.
C: Music: 'Christ lag in Todes Banden' from Walter's Geistliche Gesangbüchlein, 1524.
C: SSAATTBB arr. from "Evangelical Lutheran Hymn-Book", 1931, alt.
C: copyright: public domain.
M: 4/4
L: 1/4
Q: 1/4=110
K: C
%%staves {(V1 V2) (V3 V4) (V5 V6) (V7 V8)}
