% A1 = independent diatonic alto line derived from original alto.
% A2 = contrary-motion alto; diatonic; no accidentals.
% T1/T2 = original tenor line, diatonic (^G, → G,).
% Bar/B1 = original bass, diatonic (_B,, → B,,).
%
%  Pickup: S1=A A; S2=F F; A1=C C; A2=A, A,; T1=D D; T2=B, B,; Bar=D, D,; B1=D, D,
